          <p>
            Decide whether the graphs in <xref ref="fig_ism_H3b6_K3b3"></xref>
            are isomorphic and carefully justify your answer.
          </p>
          <figure xml:id="fig_ism_H3b6_K3b3">
            <caption>The Harary graph <m>H_{3,6}</m> and the complete bipartite graph <m>K_{3,3}</m> <xref ref="exer_show_ism_H3b6_K3b3">for</xref>.</caption>
            image type not recognized
          </figure>
        </statement>
      </exercise>
      <exercise xml:id="exer_show_nonism_order5">
        <title>\exerP</title>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Decide whether the graphs in <xref ref="fig_nonism_order5"></xref>
